{"tid":760424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★近半港人對經濟不抱樂觀　64%人料港股將大瀉","createTime":"2018-07-29T13:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T04:46:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a45985c32d17b2878a048ed1944dec7e15b3dc0a","tid":760424,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"香港區塊鏈聯會上月街頭訪問320名市民，發現在連串國際事件，例如中美貿易戰及美國對港徵收關稅的影響下，46%受訪港人對香港未來一年的經濟不抱樂觀態度，有<span style=\"color: red;\">64%人預計港股在未來一個月會大幅下跌。<br />\n</span><br />\n調查又指，香港樓市連升26個月，港府打算開徵空置稅，而居屋定價亦大幅下調，有43%受訪者認為未來一年的香港樓市會大幅下跌。綜觀所有經濟因素，<span style=\"color: red;\">68%人認為未來一年香港經濟會非常差。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180729/bkn-20180729150722493-0729_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180729%2Fbkn-20180729150722493-0729_00822_001.html&d=BVLY2Jx7JIkSF0MxOOUexpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0f4697ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180729/bkn-20180729150722493-0729_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1774eb7535b3c0f1b4ac8172f69d27a306e5df91","tid":760424,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7c2000b0161af4710fd4442df3f58317d2b393","tid":760424,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:46:02.000Z","msg":"drop to $0 :<br />\n<br />\n175<br />\n<br />\n700<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d0a8a7605b66873e6d858981552a1694a203b5","tid":760424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"大家都批評樓價高<br />\n<br />\n咁跌咪好囉, 有乜問題？"},{"pid":"3aac72ff0579d786